<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>비밀번호 재설정</title>
    </head>
    <body
        style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e8f0f0; /* 테마 배경색 */
            font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            word-break: keep-all;
        "
    >
        <table
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="background-color: #e8f0f0; min-height: 100vh"
        >
            <tr>
                <td align="center" valign="middle" style="padding: 40px 0">
                    <table
                        border="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        width="600"
                        style="
                            background-color: white;
                            border-radius: 13px;
                            box-shadow: 0px 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* 그림자 부드럽게 조정 */
                            overflow: hidden;
                            border: 1px solid white;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 60px 40px">
                                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px">
                                    <div
                                        style="
                                            color: #2d3748; /* Primary Dark Color */
                                            font-size: 28px;
                                            font-weight: 700;
                                            line-height: 1.4;
                                            margin-bottom: 16px;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        비밀번호 재설정
                                    </div>
                                    <div
                                        style="
                                            color: #718096; /* Secondary Text Color */
                                            font-size: 16px;
                                            font-weight: 500;
                                            line-height: 1.6;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        아래 버튼을 눌러 비밀번호를 재설정 해주세요.
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div style="text-align: center">
                                    <a
                                        href="<%= resetUrl %>"
                                        style="
                                            display: inline-block;
                                            width: 100%;
                                            max-width: 400px;
                                            padding: 18px 0;
                                            background-color: #ff6b6b; /* Accent Color 적용 */
                                            border-radius: 10px;
                                            text-decoration: none;
                                            color: white;
                                            font-size: 18px;
                                            font-weight: 700;
                                            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.25); /* 버튼 그림자 추가 */
                                        "
                                    >
                                        비밀번호 재설정
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; color: #a0aec0; font-size: 12px;">
                                    본 메일은 발신 전용입니다.<br>
                                    버튼이 동작하지 않는다면 링크를 복사하여 주소창에 붙여넣으세요.
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>